aa ab laut chalen ( translation : come , let 's go back ) is a 1999 indian hindi romantic drama musical directed by rishi kapoor making his directorial debut and also remains the only film he had directed in his career .   the film 's script was written by sachin bhowmick and rumi jaffery .   the film premiered in india and the united states on 22 january 1999 .   it starred rajesh khanna , akshaye khanna and aishwarya rai and was the last production of r. k. films .   the film performed poorly at the box office .